        (6012,'main','heatmap','limit','25000','Maximum Samples','text',0,'numeric','size=5','Limit the total samples of spatial data to use to generate a heatmap. The more samples allowed the more detailed a heatmap will be, but will take longer to render when created.\r\n\r\nLeave blank for the default of 5500\r\n\r\n<b>Recommendation:</b> 5000 - 10000'),
