        (2517,'main','awards','allow_partial_month','1','Calculate partial month awards?','boolean',0,NULL,'','Should awards for partial months be calculated? If enabled awards will be calculated for the month even if the current month is not yet complete. The awards will be re-calculated each time logs are processed until the 1st of the next month rolls around. At that time the awards will be calculated one last time and saved. If disabled you will never seen awards for the current month until the full month has gone by.'),
        (2518,'main','awards','allow_partial_week','1','Calculate partial week awards?','boolean',0,NULL,'','Should awards for partial weeks be calculated? If enabled awards will be calculated for the week even if the current week is not yet complete. The awards will be re-calculated each time logs are processed until the following week rolls around. At that time the awards will be calculated one last time and saved. If disabled you will never seen awards for the current week until the full week has gone by.'),
        (2520,'info','daily_maxdays','lastupdate','1220446660',NULL,'text',0,NULL,'',''),
        (2521,'main',NULL,'maxdays_exclusive','0','Max days is exclusive?','boolean',0,'','','If enabled, all stats outside of the \'max days\' range will be excluded from the compiled statistics. This setting will affect player statistics but will not change a player\'s skill value.\r\n\r\nFor example: If you have 1000 kills in the last 60 days and \'max days\' is set to 30 with this <b>enabled</b> you will lose all kills past 30 days. If <b>disabled</b> you retain all the old kills.'),
