        (2525,'theme',NULL,'weapons_dir','','Images: Weapon directory','text',0,'','','Absolute root directory where weapon images are located.\r\n\r\n<b>Recommendation:</b> Leave blank for default. (auto-discovered)'),
        (2526,'theme',NULL,'weapons_url','','Images: Weapon URL','text',0,'','','Absolute URL for weapon images. This should match up to the location of the \"Root directory for weapons\" setting. So the images can be referenced within the theme output correctly.\r\n\r\n<b>Recommendation:</b> Leave blank for default (auto-discovered)'),
